name dblfloatfix
category Package
revision 28983
shortdesc Fixes for twocolumn floats
longdesc The package solves two problems: floats in a twocolumn document
longdesc come out in the right order and allowed float positions are now
longdesc [tbp]. The package actually merges facilities from fixltx2e and
longdesc stfloats.
