name newfloat
category Package
revision 68434
shortdesc Define new floating environments
longdesc The package offers the command \DeclareFloatingEnvironment,
longdesc which the user may use to define new floating environments
longdesc which behave like the LaTeX standard foating environments
longdesc figure and table.
