name ntgclass
category Package
revision 65522
shortdesc "European" versions of standard classes
longdesc The bundle offers versions of the standard LaTeX article and
longdesc report classes, rewritten to reflect a more European design,
longdesc and the a4 package, which is better tuned to the shape of a4
longdesc paper than is the a4paper class option of the standard classes.
longdesc The classes include several for article and report
longdesc requirements, and a letter class. The elements of the bundle
longdesc were designed by members of the Dutch TeX Users Group NTG.
