name pdfcol
category Package
revision 64469
shortdesc Macros for maintaining colour stacks under pdfTeX
longdesc Since version 1.40 pdfTeX supports colour stacks. The driver
longdesc file pdftex.def for package color defines and uses a main
longdesc colour stack since version v0.04b. This package is intended for
longdesc package writers. It defines macros for setting and maintaining
longdesc new colour stacks.
