name standalone
category Package
revision 64677
shortdesc Compile TeX pictures stand-alone or as part of a document
longdesc A class and package is provided which allows TeX pictures or
longdesc other TeX code to be compiled standalone or as part of a main
longdesc document. Special support for pictures with beamer overlays is
longdesc also provided. The package is used in the main document and
longdesc skips extra preambles in sub-files. The class may be used to
longdesc simplify the preamble in sub-files. By default the preview
longdesc package is used to display the typeset code without margins.
longdesc The behaviour in standalone mode may adjusted using a
longdesc configuration file standalone.cfg to redefine the standalone
longdesc environment.
depend adjustbox
depend currfile
depend filemod
depend gincltex
depend xkeyval
