name totcount
category Package
revision 21178
shortdesc Find the last value of a counter
longdesc The package records the value that was last set, for any
longdesc counter of interest; since most such counters are simply
longdesc incremented when they are changed, the recorded value will
longdesc usually be the maximum value.
