name xltxtra
category Package
revision 56594
shortdesc "Extras" for LaTeX users of XeTeX
longdesc This package was previously used to provide a number of
longdesc features that were useful for typesetting documents with
longdesc XeLaTeX. Many of those features have now been incorporated into
longdesc the fontspec package and other packages, but the package
longdesc persists for backwards compatibility. Nowadays, loading xltxtra
longdesc will: load the fontspec, metalogo, and realscripts packages;
longdesc redefine \showhyphens so it works correctly; and define two
longdesc extra commands: \vfrac and \namedglyph.
depend metalogo
